description: Scryb Inc., a technology company, provides platform to power businesses and technologies. The company's cloud-based platform comprising sensor technology, IoT, predictive analytics, and computer vision. It serves digital health, diagnostics, cybersecurity, and manufacturing markets. The company was formerly known as Relay Medical Corp. and changed its name to Scryb Inc. in December 2021. Scryb Inc. is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
